version_year_week

with role    immune-system
with trait   archive_off solo stale
with info    good 20120609
with info    home http://sorcerer.silverice.org/
with info    cite "rubbish removal

Weekly removal of old files from:
$ARCHIVE_CACHE
$CCACHE_CACHE
$SOURCE_CACHE"

build(){ :; }
post_install(){ bash $SCRIPT_DIR/clean; }
